# Agent Files — Never Stage

Never stage or commit agent-related files to repositories.

- Never `git add` files from: .studio/, evidence/, drafts/, notepads/
- Never `git add` AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, or any agent context files
- Do NOT add these to .gitignore (that leaves traces) — simply never stage them
- Zero traces of agent tooling in repositories
